special_powers.name: MINION: REMOTE COMMAND
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Iron Man, Tony Stark, or Ultron is within 8 squares, Iron Man Drone can be given a move action as a free action, but modifies its speed value by -2.

special_powers.name: MINION: ULTRON'S SHELL
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Hank Pym or Ultron is within 8 squares, Ultron Drone can be given a move action as a free action, but modifies its speed value by -2.

special_powers.name: FOE OF THE TALL AND THE SMALL
special_powers.description: Egghead deals penetrating damage to characters that don't possess the standard damage symbol.

special_powers.name: DIMENSIONAL COPY
special_powers.description: Space Phantom can use Incapacitate. If he uses it and hits a character that's 100 points or less, choose a standard power that character possesses. Space Phantom can use that power until he uses this special power again.

special_powers.name: BIO DUPLICATE
special_powers.description: Whenever a friendly character named Madame Masque or Masque would be KO'd by an oponent's attack, you may instead turn that character's dial to its last non-KO click and KO this figure. If you do place that character in this square.

special_powers.name: MINION: MOLTEN REBIRTH
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Jinku is within 8 squares, Lava Man can use Regeneration and ignores hindering terrain for movement purposes.

special_powers.name: MINION: WE KEEP THE COUNCIL'S SECRETS
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Max Fury is within 8 squares, Shadow Council Soldier modifies his damage value by +1.

special_powers.name: DOCTOR, NOT A FIGHTER
special_powers.description: Donald Blake's combat values can't be modified.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO:THOR, GOD OF LIGHTNING
special_powers.description: Give Donald Blake a power action that deals no pushing damage and replace this character with CW #038 Thor, CW #202 Thor, or FF:CW #002 Thor on its orange starting line. If you do, after actions resolve, even if this power is lost, deal 1 damage to each adjacent opposing character. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO: IRON MAN, SHINING KNIGHT
special_powers.description: Give Tony Stark a power action that deals no pushing damage and replace this character with CW #024 Iron Man, CW #201 Iron Man, or FF:CW #001 Iron Man on its orange starting line. After actions resolve, even if this power is lost, you may move Iron Man up to 3 squares. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: HER? WELL, SHE FLIES. AND WE THINK IT'S A "HER"
special_powers.description: Dinah Soar may carry up to two characters if they both have the Avengers keyword, or three characters if they all have the Great Lakes Avengers keyword. Dinah Soar modifies her speed value by -1 for each character carried instead of the normal effects when using the Carry ability.

special_powers.name: THROUGH THE WALL
special_powers.description: Vision can use Charge and Stealth. He may use Charge normally, or be given a double power action to use Charge and ignore characters and terrain for movement purposes.

special_powers.name: MORPH: HANK PYM
special_powers.description: Give Hank Pym a move or close combat action that deals no pushing damage.  After the action resolves, replace him with any character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: TINKERER SUPREME
special_powers.description: Give Hank Pym a free action if he occupies a square with a light or heavy object, and choose a standard attack power.  He can use the chosen power this turn.

special_powers.name: MORPH: HANK PYM
special_powers.description: Give Ant-Man a move or close combat action that deals no pushing damage.  After the action resolves, replace him with any character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: PYM PARTICLES, SHRINK
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Ant-Man a free action to choose a friendly character of 75 points or less with the Avengers keyword.  That character possesses "Tiny Size" as long as this Ant-Man is on the map.

special_powers.name: ANT-SWARM
special_powers.description: Ant-Man can use Poison.  When he does, opposing characters that occupy hindering terrain are dealt 2 damage instead.

special_powers.name: MORPH: HANK PYM
special_powers.description: Give Wasp a move or close combat action that deals no pushing damage.  After the action resolves, replace him with any character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: BIO ELECTRIC BLASTS
special_powers.description: Wasp can use Incapacitate.  If he uses it and hits, deal the target 1 penetrating damage after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: CYBERNETIC WASP GOGGLES
special_powers.description: Wasp and friendly characters within 3 squares and line of fire that share a keyword with Wasp can use Exploit Weakness if their printed damage value is 2 or less.

special_powers.name: MYSTERIOUS MOTIVES
special_powers.description: If she has no action tokens, Madame Masque can use Outwit. If she has one action token, Madame Masque can use Perplex. If she has two action tokens, Madame Masque can use Enhancement.

special_powers.name: LAVAFLOW
special_powers.description: Jinku can use Phasing/Teleport. After Jinku resolves a move action, you may place one Lava hindering terrain marker in any clear square he moved through.

special_powers.name: HEAT OF THE EARTH'S CORE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, deal 1 damage to each character occupying a square with a Lava hindering terrain marker.

special_powers.name: EVERYTHING THAT NICK KNOWS
special_powers.description: Opposing characters can't use the S.H.I.E.L.D. team ability.

special_powers.name: SECRET AVENGERS COORDINATOR
special_powers.description: Sharon Carter and adjacent friendly characters with the Avengers keyword can use Stealth.

special_powers.name: RADIANT BURST
special_powers.description: Ms. Marvel can use Energy Explosion as if she had a range of 7 and 2 targets.

special_powers.name: TATICAL TARGETING
special_powers.description: When choosing targets for a ranged combat attack, Iron Man may choose both a character and an object, wall, or square of blocking terrain instead of a second character.

special_powers.name: REPULSOR RAYS
special_powers.description: After Iron Man hits a character with a ranged combat attack and actions resolve, you may knock back that character an equal amount to the difference between Iron Man's range value and the number of squares to that character.

special_powers.name: EXPLODE AND REFORM
special_powers.description: Give Nitro a double power action and make a close combat attack targeting each opposing character within 2 squares. Each character hit is dealt penetrating damage equal to 3 minus the number of squares it is from Nitro.

special_powers.name: EXPLOSIVE PUNCH
special_powers.description: Nitro can use Force Blast. He can use it normally, or as a free action to target any character that he has hit with a close combat attack this turn.

special_powers.name: OK, I'M A VOYEUR, SO WHAT?
special_powers.description: When an adjacent character moves due to its own action, once per turn you may place Ant-Man in a square adjacent to that character after the action resolves.

special_powers.name: IRREDEEMABLE LIAR
special_powers.description: Ant-Man can use Outwit, but only to counter an opposing character's Outwit or Perplex, or a special power that specificially allows the use of Outwit or Perplex.

special_powers.name: A TOUCH OF INSANITY
special_powers.description: Genis-Vell can use Perplex.  When he does, instead of the normal effects, choose +2 or -2, and roll a d6 that can't be rerolled.  Based on the result, modify the following value on the target character by the chosen amount: 1: Speed 2: Attack 3: Defense 4: Damage 5: Range 6: All Combat Values

special_powers.name: AVENGERS TWO
special_powers.description: When Wonder Man is adjacent to a friendly character named Beast, modify both their attack values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: JET BELT
special_powers.description: Wonder Man can use Charge and possesses the "Wing" symbol.

special_powers.name: TRAUMATIC HEALING
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, if Wolverine took damage since your last turn, you may heal him of 1 damage. If he's on click #8, you may heal him of 2 damage instead.

special_powers.name: THE BEST THERE IS
special_powers.description: When making a close combat attack, you may have Wolverine's attack value become the attack value of his target +1.

special_powers.name: BIO ELECTRIC BLASTS
special_powers.description: Wasp can use Incapacitate.  If she uses it and hits, deal the target 1 penetrating damage after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: INDESTRUCTIBLE EBONY BLADE
special_powers.description: Black Knight can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and Steal Energy. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: SIBLING DUO
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Scarlet Witch is adjacent to Quicksilver, modify both their attack values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: ARROGANT ASSAULT
special_powers.description: Quicksilver can use Flurry. He may use it normally, or as a free action instead of a close combat attack while using Hypersonic Speed. If he uses it in this way, modify his defense value by -1 until your next turn for each hit.

special_powers.name: NEW AVENGERS COORDINATOR
special_powers.description: Victoria Hand and adjacent friendly characters with the Avengers keyword modify their attack values by +1 if they are on their first click.

special_powers.name: TRAITOR, OR NOT?
special_powers.description: Give Victoria Hand a power action if she began the game on your force. She becomes friendly to an opponent's force. At the beginning of each of that opponent's turns, that player deals 1 unavoidable damage to another character friendly to Victoria Hand.

special_powers.name: PRESENCE OF THE GOD OF WAR
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters modify their attack values by +1. Adjacent opposing characters modify their attack values by -1.

special_powers.name: MASTER OF ALL WEAPONS
special_powers.description: Ares can use Close Combat Expert and Ranged Combat Expert. Whenever he uses one of these powers, opposing characters can't use that same power until your next turn. This power can't be countered by characters of 100 points or less.

special_powers.name: THE CONSUMING VOID INSIDE
special_powers.description: After an action resolves during which Sentry took damage from an opposing character, you may replace him with CW #045 Void on the same click number.

special_powers.name: YOU'RE JUST ANOTHER PRETTY LITTLE BIRD TO ME
special_powers.description: Tigra can use Charge and Flurry.

special_powers.name: KITTEN HAS CLAWS
special_powers.description: Tigra can use Blades/Claws/Fangs, but the minimum result of her d6 roll is 2 and her maximum result is 5.

special_powers.name: PHEROMONES
special_powers.description: Give Spider-Woman a free action. She may modify the attack value of an adjacent friendly character by +1 and she may modify the defense value of an adjacent opposing character by -1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: SUMMON ASGARDIAN BLIZZARD
special_powers.description: Characters with the "standard damage" or "tiny size" symbol can't target characters 7 or more squares away. Modify all other characters' speed values by -2 if they begin an action within 6 squares of Thor.

special_powers.name: MY CRIMINAL PAST
special_powers.description: Hawkeye can use Running Shot and Stealth.

special_powers.name: KNOCKOUT GAS ARROW
special_powers.description: Hawkeye can use Energy Explosion.  When he does, after actions resolve give one action token to each character hit by the attack.

special_powers.name: OLDER THAN I LOOK
special_powers.description: Nick Fury can use Leadership and Willpower.

special_powers.name: THE MAN WITH THE PLAN
special_powers.description: When a friendly character misses with one or more attacks, you may roll a d6 after actions resolve. On a result of a 6, you may remove an action token from that character. Nick Fury can only remove one action token per turn this way.

special_powers.name: THE THUNDERBOLTS GAMBIT
special_powers.description: When you build your force, characters that possess the Masters of Evil keyword or team ability also possess the Thunderbolts keyword. If your force also includes the Thunderbolts Additional Team Ability you must assign it to them.

special_powers.name: MEGALOMANIACAL GENIUS
special_powers.description: Baron Zemo can use Leadership, Mastermind and Outwit. He is considered 150 points when using Leadership or Mastermind if he's adjacent to a character with the Thunderbolts keyword.

special_powers.name: MY UNWITTING PAWNS
special_powers.description: Loki can use Shape Change. When Loki rolls a 6 for Shape Change, friendly characters can't be targeted by ranged attacks this turn.

special_powers.name: BLINDING STELLAR RADIATION
special_powers.description: Binary can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast. If she does and hits, the hit character can't make a ranged combat attack during its next turn.

special_powers.name: WHITE HOLE ENERGY
special_powers.description: Binary can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Regeneration.

special_powers.name: TORNADO
special_powers.description: Give Crystal a power action and choose an unoccupied square of clear terrain within range and line of fire. Crystal can use Quake as a free action as if she occupied that square.

special_powers.name: TWIN ELEMENTS: FIRESTORM
special_powers.description: When Crystal uses the Tornado trait, also deal 1 penetrating damage to each hit character after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: TWIN ELEMENTS: WATERSPOUT
special_powers.description: When Crystal uses the Tornado trait, also give an action token to each hit character with zero action tokens after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: TWIN ELEMENTS: SANDSTORM
special_powers.description: When Crystal uses the Tornado trait, after actions resolve, hit characters use Toughness instead of Invulnerability or Impervious for the rest of the turn.

special_powers.name: HE IS THE FALSE ONE!
special_powers.description: After an action resolves during which Void healed, you may replace him with CW #035 Sentry on the same click number.

special_powers.name: THE VOID ALWAYS FINDS YOU
special_powers.description: The Void can use Plasticity. Give Void a free action and place him adjacent to any character that caused Void (or a replaced Sentry) to take damage since your last turn, and then deal 1 damage to all adjacent opposing characters.

special_powers.name: LIFE UNDERGROUND
special_powers.description: When The Unspoken occupies a square on the lowest elevation of the map, he can use Leadership and Stealth.

special_powers.name: SLAVE ENGINE DEGENERATION
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within 3 squares possess Battle Fury and can't be given power actions.

special_powers.name: CREATE NEW MARAUDERS
special_powers.description: When you build your force, friendly characters possess the Marauders keyword this game if they possess the Brotherhood of Mutants or X-Men keyword or team ability.

special_powers.name: SKINSHIFTING
special_powers.description: Mr. Sinister can use Shape Change.

special_powers.name: COMPLETE CELLULAR REGENERATION
special_powers.description: Mr. Sinister can use Regeneration, Toughness, and Willpower. If he has no action tokens, Mr. Sinister may use Regeneration as a free action but subtracts 3 instead of 2.

special_powers.name: I CAN REBUILD YOU, MUTANT
special_powers.description: Mr. Sinister can use Perplex. When another friendly character possessing the Marauders keyword would be KO'd, you may roll a d6. On a result of 6, instead place them within 6 squares of Mr. Sinister and turn them to their last non-KO click, then roll another d6. Heal that character of half the result.

special_powers.name: STILL GOT THOSE PHOTOGRAPHIC REFLEXES
special_powers.description: Give Taskmaster a free action. Choose any standard power an opposing character within 8 squares and line of fire and with one or more action tokens can use. Taskmaster can use that power until the end of this turn.

special_powers.name: YOU HOLD NO SURPRISES
special_powers.description: Taskmaster's combat values can't be modified by opposing characters' powers or abilities.

special_powers.name: SUPER-VILLAIN TRAINING
special_powers.description: Taskmaster can use Enhancement and Leadership. When he succeeds on an roll for Leadership, adjacent friendly characters modify their attack and range values by +1.

special_powers.name: MY ALTERNATE AVENGERS
special_powers.description: Morgan Le Fay can use Perplex, but only to target a character with the Avengers keyword. When she does, she may use it normally, or she can modify any value except damage by +2 or -2.  An Avengers themed team may include Morgan Le Fay and is still a themed team.

special_powers.name: COLD STEEL IS MY BANE
special_powers.description: When an opposing character hits Morgan Le Fay and rolls for Blades/Claws/Fangs, add 1 to that die roll.

special_powers.name: ASTRAL FORM FADE
special_powers.description: Morgan Le Fay can use Toughness. At the beginning of your turn, choose either Combat Reflexes or Energy Shield/Deflection. Morgan Le Fay can use the chosen power until your next turn.

special_powers.name: COME BACK AFTER I'M RESTED AND TRY AGAIN
special_powers.description: Kang can use Probability Control during his own attack rolls.

special_powers.name: TIMELINE RESET
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Kang a power action.  Remove action tokens from all friendly characters that are Kang's point value or less.  Characters that already took a non-free action this turn can't take another.

special_powers.name: ENSLAVEMENT
special_powers.description: When Chaos King KO's an opposing character, after actions resolve he may use Mind Control as a free action targeting any number of other characters on the defeated character's force that total less points than the defeated character.  These characters do not need to be within range or line of fire.

special_powers.name: THE NAME IS... HAIRBALL!
special_powers.description: When Lockjaw and Hairball attacks, they may choose to knock back a hit character 2 squares after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: DON'T HIT THE CAT! OR THE DOG, REALLY
special_powers.description: Lockjaw and Hairball can use Toughness and Super Senses. When they succeed on a roll for Super Senses, after actions resolve you may knock back the attacking character 2 squares. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: LEADER OF THE PET AVENGERS... PLUS CAT
special_powers.description: Lockjaw and Hairball can use Leadership. If they succeed, they may use it to remove tokens from characters with the Animal or Pet Avengers keyword regardless of point value.

special_powers.name: BUZZING RIGHT IN YOUR EAR
special_powers.description: When an adjacent opposing character attacks Ant-Man and Wasp and misses, deal the attacking character 1 unavoidable damage after actions resolve. When a non-adjacent opposing character attacks Ant-Man and Wasp and misses, deal each opposing character adjacent to Ant-Man and Wasp 1 unavoidable damage after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: THE SHARPEST
special_powers.description: Hawkeye and Mockingbird can use the Sharpshooter ability. Opposing characters within 8 squares can't use the Sharpshooter ability.

special_powers.name: TRICK ARROWS AND BATTLE STAVES
special_powers.description: Hawkeye and Mockingbird can use Energy Explosion, Incapacitate, and Smoke Cloud. They can use these powers normally, or they may be given a power or ranged combat action as a free action instead of a ranged combat attack when using the Duo Attack ability to use one of these powers.

special_powers.name: WATCH EACH OTHER'S BACK
special_powers.description: Hawkeye and Mockingbird can use Combat Reflexes and Super Senses.

special_powers.name: KEEPING THE FAMILY SAFE
special_powers.description: Vision and Scarlet Witch can use Phasing/Teleport and Running Shot. When using Running Shot, they may ignore one character, one wall or one square of blocking terrain for movement purposes. They may use Phasing/Teleport as a free action if an opposing character caused them to take damage since your last turn.

special_powers.name: EMPOWERED HEX BOLTS
special_powers.description: Vision and Scarlet Witch can use Energy Explosion. When they do, the attack value of each hit character of 200 points or less becomes 9 if it was higher than 9, then is locked until your next turn.

special_powers.name: CHAOS MAGIC
special_powers.description: Give Scarlet Witch and Wonder Man a free action and choose an opposing character within 8 squares and line of fire and roll a d6 that can't be rerolled. The chosen character can't use the following type of powers or abilities until your next turn based on the result. 1 = Speed Powers; 2 = Attack Powers; 3 = Defense Powers; 4 = Damage Powers; 5 = Team Abilities; 6 = Your choice of any of the above

special_powers.name: IONIC PUNCH AND HEX BOLTS
special_powers.description: Scarlet Witch and Wonder Man deal penetrating damage to characters 150 points or more.

special_powers.name: EMERGENT EVIL
special_powers.description: Sentry and Void can use Multiattack ability. Give Sentry and Void a power action if it has no tokens and replace it with CW #035 Sentry or CW #045 Void on the same click number. When the replacement character would be KO'd, you may instead return this character to the map on click #10.

special_powers.name: ASGARD MUST FALL
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Sentry and Void a double power action.  For the rest of the game even if this power is lost elevated terrain is considered grounded hindering terrain. Deal Sentry and Void and each character occupying elevated terrain 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: AFTER ULTIMATE POWER
special_powers.description: Give Dr. Doom and Kang a power action. Place them adjacent to the highest point opposing character on the map, then use the Duo Attack ability as a free action targeting that character for each attack.

special_powers.name: INEVITABLE BETRAYAL
special_powers.description: When this click is revealed for the first time in a game, stop turning the dial and choose Dr. Doom or Kang. For the rest of the game, even if this power is lost, this character now possesses "standard attack symbol" and if you chose Dr. Doom, this character can use Outwit, or if you chose Kang, this character can use Probability Control.

special_powers.name: MY RIVAL
special_powers.description: When making a duo attack, if the first attack misses, modify Thor and Hercules' combat values by +1 for the second attack.

special_powers.name: MY BROTHER
special_powers.description: Thor and Hercules can use Invulnerability. Modify their defense value by +1 for each time they have been attacked this turn. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: TRIO ATTACK
special_powers.description: Give Avengers Prime a double power action. They can be given 3 close or ranged combat actions as free actions, each targeting a single character. These free actions may be used to activate the same effect.

special_powers.name: IRON MAN IN THE VANGUARD
special_powers.description: Avengers Prime can use Perplex, Ranged Combat Expert, and Running Shot.

special_powers.name: CAP IN THE LEAD
special_powers.description: Avengers Prime can use Energy Shield/Deflection, Incapacitate, and Leadership.

special_powers.name: THOR AT THE FOREFRONT
special_powers.description: Avengers Prime can use Charge, Close Combat Expert, and Energy Explosion.

special_powers.name: CONTROL OF THE WORLD'S COMPUTERS
special_powers.description: Vision can use Phasing/Teleport. Once per turn, if the number 6 comes up on a die for an attack roll when an opposing character attacks Vision, you may force an opponent to reroll that die. When an opposing character with the Armor or Robot keyword attacks Vision, modify Vision's defense value by +2.

special_powers.name: ULTRA-VISION
special_powers.description: Vision can use Impervious. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: FUTURE FOUNDATION
special_powers.description: Friendly characters possessing the Fantastic Four team ability can't use that team ability.  Instead, they can use the following team ability: FUTURE FOUNDATION TA: When a character using this team ablility takes 2 or more damage from an opponent's attack, give the attacking character an action token after actions resolve.  If you can't, deal them 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: WORLD'S SMARTEST MAN..EVEN WHEN THERE'S MORE OF ME
special_powers.description: Mr. Fantastic can use Outwit and deals penetrating damage to characters that can use Outwit.  This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: THE PEACEMAKER
special_powers.description: When she's adjacent to exactly one friendly character and one opposing character, you may give Invisible Woman a free action to heal both characters 1 click.

special_powers.name: MORPH: HANK PYM
special_powers.description: Give Ant-Man a move or close combat action that deals no pushing damage.  After the action resolves, replace him with any character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: PYM PARTICLES, GROW
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Giant-Man a free action to choose a friendly character of 75 points or less with the Avengers keyword.  That character possesses "Giant Damage Symbol" as long as Giant-Man is on the map.

special_powers.name: SWAT
special_powers.description: When given a close combat action, Giant-Man may target all opposing characters within two squares and then divide the damage between them.  This power can't be countered by characters 100 points or less.

special_powers.name: AVENGERS, BEHIND ME!
special_powers.description: Giant-Man can use Defend and Toughness.

special_powers.name: BUILDING SHOVE
special_powers.description: Give Giant-Man a power action if he is adjacent to elevated terrain.  All characters occupying that level of elevated terrain within that same continuous border are dealt 1 penetrating damage and knocked back 1 square.

special_powers.name: MORPH: HANK PYM
special_powers.description: Give Giant-Man a move or close combat action that deals no pushing damage.  After the action resolves, replace him with any character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: PYM PARTICLES, GROW
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Giant-Man a free action to choose a friendly character of 75 points or less with the Avengers keyword.  That character possesses "Giant Damage Symbol" as long as Giant-Man is on the map.

special_powers.name: YOU'RE UNDER ARREST!
special_powers.description: Iron Man can use Incapacitate as if he had 3 targets.

special_powers.name: DIRECTOR STARK
special_powers.description: Iron Man can use Enhancement and Willpower.

special_powers.name: ART THOU TOO CRAVEN TO FIGHT?
special_powers.description: Give Thor a free action if he has no action tokens and choose an opposing character within Thor's range and line of fire that is not adjacent to any other characters. During its next turn, that character must attack Thor or be given a move action.

special_powers.name: I AM NO MORTAL!
special_powers.description: Thor can use Toughness and Willpower.

special_powers.name: THE SUIT
special_powers.description: Captain America can use Toughness.

special_powers.name: SHIELD SLASH
special_powers.description: When Captain America makes a ranged attack and the result of the attack roll is doubles, he deals penetrating damage. When Captain America makes a ranged attack and the attack roll is 10 or higher, give an action token to all hit characters after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: DIMENSION SWAP
special_powers.description: Space Phantom can use Outwit, but only to target characters within his range and line of fire without the Deity keyword. When he does, he can use that countered standard power as long as it's countered.

special_powers.name: ADJUSTABLE MATTER SCAN
special_powers.description: Vision can use Phasing/Teleport. Characters he targets with an attack can't use Shape Change or Super Senses for that attack.

special_powers.name: SYNTHEZOID CONSTRUCT
special_powers.description: Vision can use Super Senses and Toughness.

special_powers.name: HEROIC SACRIFICE
special_powers.description: When an adjacent friendly character would be dealt damage but before it takes the damage, you may KO Masque. If you do, that character ignores that damage.

special_powers.name: ENERGY REDIRECTION
special_powers.description: If Ms. Marvel was targeted by a ranged combat attack since your last turn, she can use Exploit Weakness and Penetrating/Psychic Blast as if she had a range value of 6.

special_powers.name: SUMMON THE DRONES
special_powers.description: Give Ultron a free action if she has no action tokens. Put a CW #002 Iron Man Drone or CW #003 Ultron Drone in your starting area on its 30 point line if less than 4 total friendly characters with those names are on the map.

special_powers.name: 110111 ERROR REBOOT
special_powers.description: Ultron can use Regeneration and Super Senses. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: MORE THAN HUMAN
special_powers.description: Spider-Woman can use Leap/Climb.

special_powers.name: DOUBLE AGENT
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose either Hydra or S.H.I.E.L.D. Spider-Woman can use that team ability this game.

special_powers.name: BARREL OVER
special_powers.description: When Wonder Man hits an opposing character with an attack, after actions resolve he may move 2 squares (breaking away automatically) and target a different opposing character with a close combat attack as a free action.
This character can use Force Blast and Invulnerability.

When used in a close combat attack, modify the attacker's damage value by +3 instead of +2.  This object can't be thrown. Characters less than 100 points can't hold this object.  This object can't be the target of Telekinesis. This object can't be destroyed by an attack targeting it for 3 damage, it requires 4 or more.
